tossup_question: 16) MATH  The jukebox is broken! The probability that any song plays properly is 1/n, where n is the length of the song in minutes. What is the probability that Danny, who likes to party, can play a 2 minute song followed by a 3 minute song without any interruptions?
bonus_question: 16) MATH  A rectangle is inscribed in a circle with radius 5. What is the area of the rectangle if its sides are in a 1:2 ratio?
